Thus to make this symmetric we need $ cÌƒ_n := c_n Î±_{n+1}/Î±_n = Î±_n/Î±_{n+1} =: bÌƒ_n$, i.e., $Î±_{n+1} = Î±_n/\sqrt{c_n}$,
